                            Amstrad CPC Games F.A.Q.
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

F10 is the quit key for both Amstrad emulators.

To run a game...
----------------
1. Select a disk from the file requester.
2. Type 'cat' on Amstrad screen.
3. Find the file you want to run.
4. Type 'run"{filename}' where {filename} is the program you
   want to run. e.g run"star.bas will run Starquake

Speed Regulation
----------------
1. Turn of JIT
2. Increase the CPU Speed in the emulator settings to get the right speed.
